{"word":"Dust","slug":"dust","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Dust</b> - <b>(1)</b> Man made from<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=7'>Gen 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=19'>Gen 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=27'>Gen 18:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=10&verse=9'>Job 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=34&verse=15'>Job 34:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=103&verse=14'>Psa 103:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=12&verse=7'>Ecc 12:7</a><p/><b>(2)</b> Thrown or Shaken off in Anger<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=14'>Mat 10:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=51'>Act 13:51</a><p/><b>(3)</b> Placed on the Head as a Sign of Grief<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=6'>Jos 7:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=2&verse=12'>Job 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=10'>Lam 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=30'>Eze 27:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=19'>Rev 18:19</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Sackcloth,<b> 1950</b>"}]}